Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the first issue, there's not much we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel a bit more confident about this investigation if you asked Satoshi and Ibara as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd prefer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we can't solve the mystery, it'll be ancient history soon enough.{時効になる}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,History?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask Fukube and Mayaka for their assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me find out what happened to my uncle 45 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your uncle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.86,0:00:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That epic from the past, full of heroism and hidden tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.37,0:01:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To think, we might uncover the truth 45 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I was just researching that period myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.58,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you? Well, this picture makes me curious as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's some meaning to it, I'd also like to find out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.17,0:01:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty exciting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if we do this right, it could be the topic of this year's anthology.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make this investigation into an official club activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And thus, investigating the past has become the utmost priority for all Classics Club members.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.77,0:01:34.24,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}Bored, sitting on the windowsill,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:42.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I frown at the wind to hide my awkwardness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:50.46,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(280,0)\blur3\t(0,989,2,\blur0.5)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:55.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I nod uncertainly as I shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:02:01.26,OP,,0,0,0,,the future in my hands feeling mighty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:06.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}I feel that the wind is bringing change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.81,0:02:11.52,OP,,0,0,0,,I guess that's your fault for calling out to my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:18.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)}The cloudy sky tells a tale of what's to come
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:27.12,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)}Spread our wings with more courage than ever before
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:31.71,OP,,0,0,0,,Light and dark are still vague in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:38.01,OP,,0,0,0,,but still we want to know the reason behind kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.55,OP,,0,0,0,,No one so far has ever reached
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.43,OP,,0,0,0,,the shining distance far beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:54.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}Let's get there before the past takes it all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:03.57,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1482,473)\blur2\pos(926,557)\clip(586,554,603,599)\t(0,1482,\clip(586,554,1280,599)\t(4485,5000,\clip(1280,554,1280,599)}Past Days of the Classics Club and Its Glory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, honey! Wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Have you no shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you manage to get some documents together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you? Did you come up with a good topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to hearing your theory as to what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap. Was I supposed to prepare a theory, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chitanda family's full of rich farmers, so their Kamiyama mansion is top class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you enjoying yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am! I love cycling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Going head-on against the wind with nothing but the power of my legs! And—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. Your high school life in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that "colorful" business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that most people around me live colorful lives as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,More like, neon bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess. But you're pretty dull by comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've heard that one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I don't look down on you for that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm neon bright by nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so just being "colorful" doesn't really work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't settled for that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking because you see how busy I am with the Council and the Handicrafts Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever I do, I'll always be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tone myself down to fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If I looked down on you, instead of "dull" I'd say you had no personality at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can live without your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how did your midterms go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Average marks on every one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect from Your Dullness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Chitanda mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. The girls will be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't you expecting servants to show up and greet us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! Come in. We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit down wherever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen someone look so out of place in a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, shall we begin the investigation meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'd like to focus on what happened in the Classics Club 45 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can find out the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to include it in this year's anthology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, the gathered data and reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, any questions regarding them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Following that, your theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, I'd like to closely evaluate those theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a good chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, the first report...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should we start from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Chitanda, you start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess. Then let's go around from me in clockwise order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I investigated the second issue of {\i1}Hyouka{\i0} itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The only part with any mention of what happened 45 years ago is the introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've summarized the important facts on the second sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:21.04,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\fad(781,433)\blur0.6\t(1657,2116,\fscx140\fscy140\blur0.8)\move(582,28,598,4,1657,2116)}1) Sekitani has left us (but who did he leave?)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.91,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\fad(781,392)\blur0.6\pos(580,113)}2.) 45 years ago he was a hero, 44 years ago he was a legend
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.91,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\fad(781,392)\blur0.6\pos(684,257)}3.) He was a "quiet fighter" and a "kind hero"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.91,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\fad(781,392)\blur0.6\pos(589,341)}4) He coined the name "Hyouka"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.91,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\fad(781,392)\blur0.6\pos(695,433)}5.) There was a sacrifice in the fight (was it my uncle?)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one is about my uncle, Sekitani Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He left Kamiyama High without graduating,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so the highest level of education he completed was middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.01,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\fad(818,853)\fs55\t(2904,3840,\fscx70\fscy70)\move(618,7,618,33,2904,3821)}2.) 45 years ago he was a hero, 44 years ago he was a legend
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the second one refers to how stories become exaggerated over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:41.77,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(580,113)}2.) 45 years ago he was a hero, 44 years ago he was a legend
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:41.77,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(690,249)}3.) He was a "quiet fighter" and a "kind hero"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:41.77,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(589,341)}4) He coined the name "Hyouka"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:41.77,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(695,433)}5.) There was a sacrifice in the fight (was it my uncle?)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:41.77,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\pos(586,28)}1) Sekitani has left us (but who did he leave?)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The third and fifth are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He was quiet and kind, and he first became a fighter, then a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.65,0:07:50.86,sheet,,0,0,0,,{\1a&H30&\blur0.8\fs55\t(3069,4195,\fsp5)\move(688,193,688,564,3069,4195)}4) He coined the name "Hyouka"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth is quite interesting, but let's put it aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the end of my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ignore the part that says, "it was nothing even close to an epic"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:59.70,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\1a&H10&\blur0.6\b1\fs80\fnpastel\c&H2A2523&\frz16.41\pos(445,301)}epic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the writer's own interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they meant that it wasn't all so glorious, but more of a dirty fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for my hypothesis:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle confronted something, and as a result he had to leave the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,One other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I considered a few other things in addition to those five points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, this part about how "one year has passed."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle left the school around the time of the Kan'ya fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As a side note,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from a friend of mine who studies at another school
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was an incident at last year's fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard of those troublemakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people who like to threaten the sellers, and make off with their profits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there are always people like that at fairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps that year my uncle was unfortunate enough to be targeted,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and he tried to resist by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be how he became a{n} hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He took responsibility and left the school,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the students he left behind wrote this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me why!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when you first suggested making an anthology, do you remember what I wanted to do instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... A stall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. But you said that stalls are traditionally disallowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much money to be made at the Kan'ya Fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so why would troublemakers turn up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There are probably some who'd turn up even without the promise of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you even trying, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I'm sure we'd all love to hear what {\i1}you{\i0} think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, believe it or not, there were no such troublemakers 45 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I mention the 1960s, what comes to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo... The National Diet Building...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Placards... Demonstrations...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, Satoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The student movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of school violence that Chitanda mentioned was hardly present in the 1960s.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't fight the schools or their teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,they fought the state and the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk as if you were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I did some research into that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I forgot to consider the political climate of that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The data I gathered doesn't fit your theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm next, so I don't really know how much detail I should go into...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn Ibara and her pointless chatter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's put my theory aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How about yours, Mayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My legs are numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This mansion is really huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a pond in your garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Can I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, time for a change of scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather is just perfect on the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A pond, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.93,eyecatch small,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\pos(274,200)}The time when awns bear seeds.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.89,0:11:07.39,eyecatch big,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,641)\blur1.5\pos(644,62)}Awn Grain
