Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a "class war" during June of the previous year,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:44.80,signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fnObelixPro\fscx150\c&H090F10&}June
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was led by none other than the Classics Club's president, Sekitani Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.23,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fnObelixPro\fs75\blur1\c&H091111&\pos(646,70)}Acti{\c&H3541A4&}vi{\c&H061010&}sm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, their activism caused trouble for the teachers.
