Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, so that word means "class war" and not just "fight", huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole {\i1}Salute and Solidarity{\i0} thing is pretty fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying that this document is fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,just that it was written by someone immersed in the student movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Just thinking out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, here's my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I refute Chi's hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,According to {\i1}Salute and Solidarity{\i0}, the incident was in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was bad enough that he had to leave the school, violence must have been involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the students led by Sekitani Jun went like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave the teachers a good whacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know if they actually beat the teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but 45 years ago something threatened the autonomy of the students, and they resisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you're getting at, Mayaka, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your point is that the students resisted the teachers' oppression with violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your theory is too abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't learn anything more from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's objective, but is it controversial?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:18.73,herp,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\pos(360,3)}Hyouka
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:19.86,herp,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\pos(927,2)}Salute and Solidarity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If we believe both {\i1}Hyouka{\i0} and {\i1}Salute and Solidarity{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then the incident happened in June, but he wasn't expelled until October.
