Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:23.11,herp,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\blur0.7\c&H3E4140&\pos(952,297)}October
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If he was to be punished for a violent incident, he would've been expelled right after, in June.
