Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm wondering about that four-month difference as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It said a year had passed as of the fair, so he'd probably been expelled in October.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure like to nitpick, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we're heading in the right direction, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's it for me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you. Then, next up is—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I got kinda hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've been nibbling sweets all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're okay with rice balls, I'll make lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, is there anything we can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A handmade lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuku, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayaka, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My data sort of conflicts with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the {\i1}Kami High Monthly{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Tougaito did say they were nearing the 500th issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through the older issues of the {\i1}Kami High Monthly{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only one that mentioned what happened 45 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.67,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The second sheet contains my summary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:02.42,eyecatch small,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fs50\pos(610,48)\c&H314268&}- There was no violence involved.\N\N\N\N\N{\c&H57688D&}- It influenced the whole school.\N\N\N\N\N{\c&H455475&}- There was a united group ("us") at the center.\N\N\N\N\N{\c&H33485D&}- They used non-violent disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The first and the last point say the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.42,eyecatch small,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fs50\pos(610,48)\c&H314268&\alpha&HFF&}- There was no violence involved.\N\N\N\N\N{\alpha&H00&\c&H57688D&}- It influenced the whole school.\N\N\N\N\N{\c&H455475&}- There was a united group ("us") at the center.\N\N\N\N\N{\alpha&HFF\c&H33485D&}- They used non-violent disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.42,eyecatch small,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fs50\c&H314268&\alpha&H00&\t(0,482,\fscx120\fscy120\c&H20274B&)\move(610,48,610,17,23,482)}- There was no violence involved.\N\N\N\N\N{\alpha&HFF&\c&H57688D&}- It influenced the whole school.\N\N\N\N\N{\c&H455475&}- There was a united group ("us") at the center.\N\N\N\N\N{\alpha&HFF\c&H33485D&}- They used non-violent disobedience.
