Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no violence involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,which derails Mayaka's theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, if the usage of "us" refers to the whole school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.68,eyecatch small,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs50\c&H7C8171&\pos(592,259)}whole school         {\alpha&HFF&\t(736,778,\alpha&H00&)}"us"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that means that the whole student body was involved in the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Or failing that, it was at least led by someone supported by the whole student body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I made some with plum, kelp, and leaf mustard{takana} filling.{oxford comma service}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you grow this rice yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any questions, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this "legendary movement" was the same one Sekitani Jun was involved in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This paper alone doesn't really explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? I've got no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who knows?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's indirect proof, though.
