Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd refer to this "legendary movement" in more specific terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Just what I wanted to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good, Mayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's hear your theory, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My theory, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chitanda, but I can't come up with a theory on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The most I can do is reconcile Ibara's theory with the new facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a database can't draw conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew he'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki, please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou, is this what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kamiyama High School: Fifty Years of History{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspected some of the details might not have been kept in public records.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But looking at it again, there's nothing really worthy of mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I have no theory. What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Houtarou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget the procedure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Start from the summary, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do I really have to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot that we're drying shiitake mushrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to take them in right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, could I use the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Just go straight down that corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Suffering from page fright?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.85,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She did this much research, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I could put my head to use for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}45 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened to Sekitani Jun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Four sources,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}connected by...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The student movement... A violent incident... The time before he was expelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}45 years ago... Sekitani Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure took your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I didn't prepare a theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's just skip that and continue to the summary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Houtarou, you figured something out, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess. It's one explanation, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You figured something out, Oreki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Chitanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let us all down, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's go through everything in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First, when was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:40.49,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\blur1\fad(318,0)\fnCentury Schoolbook\b1\c&HA8C3C0&\pos(635,180)}45 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,45 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is, what was the time of year?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If we believe both {\i1}Hyouka{\i0} and {\i1}Salute and Solidarity{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,then the incident was in June,
